Note:
Mobile Navigation Components Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides comprehensive navigation components optimized for mobile interfaces.
Includes navigation bars, tab bars, breadcrumbs, and mobile-specific navigation patterns
with touch-friendly interactions and platform-specific styling for iOS and Android.

Key Features:
- Platform-native navigation bars (iOS/Android)
- Customizable tab bars with badges and icons
- Breadcrumb navigation for hierarchical content
- Search bars integrated with navigation
- Action buttons and overflow menus
- Back button handling and gestures
- Title animations and transitions
- Status bar integration
- Safe area compliance
- Accessibility support
- Dark mode and theming
- RTL layout support

Provides complete navigation component system for building intuitive mobile
application navigation with platform-specific behavior and appearance.
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors
Import "collections" as Collections

